<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>MBA Notes Hub</title>
<style>
body{font-family:Arial, sans-serif;margin:0;background:#f4f6fb}
header{background:#2b3a67;color:white;padding:20px;text-align:center}
nav{background:#1f2a4a;padding:10px;text-align:center}
nav a{color:white;margin:0 15px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:bold}
.container{width:90%;max-width:1000px;margin:auto;padding:20px}
.card{background:white;padding:20px;margin:15px 0;border-radius:10px;box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1)}
footer{background:#1f2a4a;color:white;text-align:center;padding:15px;margin-top:30px}
.button{display:inline-block;background:#2b3a67;color:white;padding:10px 15px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;margin-top:10px}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
<h1>MBA Notes Hub</h1>
<p>Simple Notes for MBA Students</p>
</header>

<nav>
<a href="#">Home</a>
<a href="#notes">MBA Notes</a>
<a href="#download">Download PDFs</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

<div class="container">

<div class="card" id="notes">
<h2>Financial Management Notes</h2>
<p>Learn the basics of financial management including meaning, objectives, functions and sources of finance in simple words.</p>
<a class="button" href="#">Read Notes</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Business Ethics Notes</h2>
<p>Simple explanations of Indian ethos, ethics in management, and corporate responsibility with examples.</p>
<a class="button" href="#">Read Notes</a>
</div>

<div class="card">
<h2>Statistics for MBA</h2>
<p>Understand statistics concepts like mean, median, mode, and business statistics with easy examples.</p>
<a class="button" href="#">Read Notes</a>
</div>

<div class="card" id="download">
<h2>Download Notes PDF</h2>
<p>You can upload your own PDF notes here for students to download.</p>
<a class="button" href="#">Download Sample PDF</a>
</div>

<div class="card" id="contact">
<h2>Contact</h2>
<p>Email: yourname@email.com</p>
<p>Instagram: @yourpage</p>
</div>

</div>

<footer>
<p>© 2026 MBA Notes Hub | Made for Students</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
